I was lookin through and noticed hunting guides and stuff but none for PvP....I play on Sullon Zek and half these guides wont work for me so Im makin one for people who also have my problem. Heres how I did 1-34.....
1-6 Gfay, killed everything but orcs so I didnt ruin faction, since I wasnt abled to be Pk'd I got a kick outta wathcin goods run up and try to kill me :-D.

6-10, FoB pit

11-19 Kurns Tower, cept for the occasional PK was good xp....at higher lvls Id get group and go down into sewers of kurns.

20-24, OT....hunted by mudpool I believe...got a PK once and awhile but no biggie.

25-28, Giants fort in WW....good xp and NO PKS the whole time.

29-32, Brute Tunnel next to Dalnir....awesome xp and good drops so made money for spells and such.

33-34, at 33 I solod in Seru alot not many pks if u stick off to side instead of right next to tunnel, and I do alot of LDON to.....

SO thats where im at now, if anyone knos somewhere else I can go please do share....

